        {
            "title": "歐洲央行6月升息可能性大增 能源壓力成關鍵",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7vsPtL1T0bhwOtrhhdrpEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_4_M_1440048337.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 據彭博新聞社和路透社週四報導,引述知情人士消息稱,除非伊朗衝突結束且能源價格回落至戰前水平,否則<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"歐洲央行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:歐洲央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐洲央行\">歐洲央行</a>決策者很可能在6月的下次會議上加息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息人士告訴路透社,如果霍爾木茲海峽的交通中斷持續,且布蘭特原油現貨價格維持在每桶100美元以上,歐洲央行可能從6月開始實施至少兩次加息。知情人士要求匿名討論私人會談內容。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲央行週四維持利率不變,將存款利率保持在2%。行長克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示,未來六週將是評估經濟狀況的適當時機,以便根據經過驗證和重新審視的資訊做出明智決定。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-446e487b-7a85-318c-b2be-f6c957bc563f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據一位消息人士透露,部分決策者在週四的會議上主張加息。討論主要集中在6月,幾乎沒有分歧認為除非前景出現根本性變化,否則有必要採取政策行動,該消息人士表示。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">官員們將在6月的下次會議上收到最新預測,屆時經濟學家和投資者預計他們會選擇加息25個基點。歐洲央行發出了對通脹日益擔憂的信號,因為霍爾木茲海峽燃料和其他產品流通的中斷推高了能源進口型歐元區的成本。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C6%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%87%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7%E5%A4%A7%E5%A2%9E-%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E6%88%90%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5-163713232.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-01 01:07:26",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價震盪加劇！伊朗揚言報復美軍 持續封鎖荷姆茲海峽",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uKbqUEDTSRtb1VKuoUmLMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/0de7ade9e311a1ddf740b1a3c774f145\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
